d by the Secretary of Defense may administer any oath” for “Any commissioned officer of any component of an armed force, whether or not on active duty, may administer any oath” in introductory provisions."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
